                           "type":"open-ended",
                           "points":2,
                           "correctAnswer":"The combination is diverging because the total power is negative (-6 D)."
                        }
                     ],
                     "correctAnswer":"i) +4 D; ii) -10 D; iii) -6 D; iv) The combination is diverging"
                  }
               ],
               "correctAnswer":"a) Completed diagram; b) Ray diagram; c) i) +4 D; ii) -10 D; iii) -6 D; iv) The combination is diverging"
